{"tid":1933453,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"摩洛哥突封領空 逾百港人滯留","createTime":"2020-03-19T09:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T10:02:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"21c68bdcb01d3a29070c42ba6ef865a76ad2f697","tid":1933453,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:47:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200319/O6ED52NQVTOXE7HGWAPNYWS2EI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200319%2FO6ED52NQVTOXE7HGWAPNYWS2EI%2F&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=d7bd9b7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200319%2FO6ED52NQVTOXE7HGWAPNYWS2EI%2F&h=5e82e6c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200319/O6ED52NQVTOXE7HGWAPNYWS2EI/</a><br />\n<br />\n摩洛哥突封領空 逾百港人滯留<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200319/large/1584546434_8688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200319%2Flarge%2F1584546434_8688.jpg&h=afd4cfed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n摩洛哥日前宣佈鎖國，旅客紛紛湧到機場趕回家。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武肺蔓延全球封關，摩洛哥周日無預警下鎖國，關閉領空及海路邊境，禁止歐亞等25國旅客入境，令逾百港人滯留當地，涉及至少四個旅行團約80名旅客及約60名自由行旅客，旅行社希望政府派包機接港人返港。入境處則接獲146名港人求助，包括70名旅行團團員。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：無外遊患者為蘭桂坊常客<br />\n<br />\n旅社盼政府派包機協助<br />\n<br />\n旅議會總幹事陳張樂怡表示，目前有四個旅行團約80名旅客滯留摩洛哥，原定陸續於本月21至23日返抵香港，現時等候政府安排；議會亦接獲通知，有約60名身處當地的自由行旅客已向入境處求助，合計至少140名港人滯留。入境處回覆指，截至昨下午6時，共接獲146名港人有關返港行程的求助，其中70人是旅行團成員。<br />\n<br />\n有20名旅客滯留當地的金怡假期主席葉慶寧表示，旅行社會設法協助團友返港，但當地機場封閉，周邊地區亦陸續封城，取道返港不易，業界希望港府派出包機到摩洛哥卡薩布蘭卡（Casablanca）接回港人。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員公民黨譚文豪表示，接獲57名滯留自由行旅客求助，他們主要滯留在非斯（Fes）及卡薩布蘭卡，有人嘗試購買機票前往歐洲，亦有人計劃經直布羅陀搭渡輪到西班牙再轉機返港。譚批評摩洛哥政府突然鎖國令旅客大失預算，尤其是對西班牙封關會增加旅客離開的難度。<br />\n<br />\n一名滯留港人在專頁「Aisha 摩洛哥之天方夜譚」撰文指，摩洛哥3月15號封閉所有國際航班，「真係好變態，即封，係走都走唔到」，慨嘆「唔知向邊到求救。大使館？冇做到咩，話有消息會話畀大家知&hellip;&hellip;變咗孤兒仔咁」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者袁楚雙"},{"pid":"9bc20903ae0d0588651bdc31840169379e4ab4dc","tid":1933453,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:48:58.000Z","msg":"WFC"},{"pid":"5a278a25a611f91fe039fca61413d478eea26346","tid":1933453,"uid":213877,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:49:46.000Z","msg":"即係政府包機都無撚用，屌你老母，做得太好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13dab3ec7a403aaf3747e8da3836f7c24d10ee90","tid":1933453,"uid":75765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:49:59.000Z","msg":"marrakesh 機場幾靚"},{"pid":"93c2b653166c9014572b564fb6206ad0af26c812","tid":1933453,"uid":213877,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:50:33.000Z","msg":"旅遊撚： 買左機票，唔通唔去咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1d50b1fead8f6850b051e27c6dfb64c70f295b","tid":1933453,"uid":42188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有20名旅客滯留當地的<span style=\"color: red;\">金怡假期</span>主席葉慶寧表示，旅行社會設法協助團友返港</blockquote>藍店都幫襯，抵啦<br />\n你話我blame the victims 都係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325f7d8dad93751f331d25ed01178183eb11641b","tid":1933453,"uid":48458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:52:20.000Z","msg":"三月歐洲經已爆到加零一仲去佢附近玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫旅行社book船去英國走啦"},{"pid":"4a3a2d144ab1c1cfa0e26f474bf6c8a3f5c53865","tid":1933453,"uid":159313,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"93c2b653166c9014572b564fb6206ad0af26c812","tid":1933453,"uid":213877,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:50:33.000Z","msg":